# Legacy laravel-admin area (src/app/Admin/**)

- This is **legacy admin** (`encore/laravel-admin` / `z-song/laravel-admin`) being migrated to Filament.
- Keep changes minimal and migration-friendly:
  - Prefer extracting reusable domain logic into `App\` services/models instead of growing legacy controllers.
  - Avoid large refactors unless they directly support a migration step.
- Note: `src/app/Admin/` is excluded from PHPStan (`src/phpstan.neon`), so rely on careful typing and runtime coverage when changing code here.
